data.description: Take a look at this larger home on a corner lot in Southlawn North. The three bedrooms, two bathrooms, formal dining or second living make this home functional and spacious. There are so many great features in this home including an awesome kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter space, glass tiled back-splash and bar for bar stools. Kitchen opens into the large living room with stone fireplace. Large windows for plenty of natural light throughout, master bedroom with two closets, crown molding and built-ins. Can't forget about the laundry room/ walk-in pantry with French doors! New water heater and new dishwasher installed in 2021. MOTIVATED SELLERS OFFERING CLOSING COST HELP!
